text: Spüligbach is a river of Lower Saxony, Germany. The Spüligbach springs southeast of , a district of Halle. It is a right tributary of the Lenne at , a district of Bodenwerder. ==See also== *List of rivers of Lower Saxony ==References== Category:Rivers of Lower Saxony Category:Rivers of Germany
